            <TITLE>
               <P>RFI 180006 — Consultancy for Job Evaluation and Grading</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>1800251</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="79414000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>After 14 years of rapid growth, the University of Luxembourg wishes to adapt its HR policy and to align it with new needs that have emerged over the last few years. This project aims at:</P>
               <P>1) Developing Job descriptions in order to:</P>
               <P>— Clarify roles and responsibilities,</P>
               <P>— Align roles with institutional goals and the changing needs of the University of Luxembourg Creating a Job structure/classification based on a proven grading methodology. </P>
               <P>2) Developing a state of the art pay structure and comp and ben policy to:</P>
               <P>— Increase transparency and set fair salary structures (internal and external equity).</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
